Please proceed the following steps to Install
---------------------------------------------
Requirements:

	a) Must be a Linux/Unix/POSIX server
	b) Must need root shell(bash) access
	c) Must need 200 MB of free space in your server
	
i) Check if yum in installed or not in the server. If there is no yum,
 please make sure automake,autoconf and libtools are installed.
 It is reccommend to configure the distribution specific  yum.	

i) Download the latest version of tar ball ffmpeginstaller.X.X.X.tar.gz , where X.X.X is the version
	# tar -xvzf ffmpeginstaller.X.X.X.tar.gz
	#cd ffmpeginstaller.X.X.X/
	# ./install
 

Project Home Page: http://www.ffmpeginstaller.com/
TECHNICAl SUPPORT:
	Get free forum support from http://forum.syslint.com/forum/20/help-and-tech-support/

